63
00:03:35,789 --> 00:03:40,627
but most vaccines protect us
for years, or even a lifetime.

64
00:03:40,628 --> 00:03:42,929
But, there's a catch.

65
00:03:42,930 --> 00:03:46,666
Like everything in life,
